00:03:18.883 --> 00:03:20.181
This is gonna be a-sub-2 times 0,

00:03:20.181 --> 00:03:21.115
that's gonna be 0.

00:03:21.115 --> 00:03:22.251
That's gonna be 0, that's gonna be 0,

00:03:22.251 --> 00:03:23.265
that's gonna be 0.

